            <title>Apple 新廣告：iPhone 15 有足夠容量    「最低 128GB 起有足夠空間儲存相片」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/iphone-15-storage-dont-let-me-go/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-15-storage-dont-let-me-go</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/iphone-15-storage-dont-let-me-go/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Don't Let Me Go]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225295</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近， Apple 推出一篇全新廣告，用戶不用為儲存容量不足而煩惱，要用家放心，iPhone 15 提供 128GB 容量起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1225296 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/w1200-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/w1200-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/w1200.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 推出新廣告暗示 iPhone 15 用 128GB 的版本已足夠，不用為儲存容量不足而煩惱</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 最近推出名為 iPhone 15 Storage | Don&#8217;t Let Me Go 的 30 秒廣告，一名男子因 iPhone 裡面有太多相片，煩惱著要刪除相片，但相片就唱出「不要讓我離開（Don&#8217;t Let Me Go）」。隨即字幕打出「放心，這是 iPhone 15，有很多容量給你收納很多相片」，而影片下面的影片介紹中，就提到 iPhone 容量由 128GB 起。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">iPhone 15 標準版儲存空間分別有 128GB、256GB 及 512GB，但 iPhone 15 主相機有 4800 萬像素，影片及相片質素高，使用更多儲存空間，再加上現時不少應用程式都佔據大量空間，128GB 是否夠用就要問問今時今日的手機用家了。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51387"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bks2zGnssMY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bks2zGnssMY">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/15/apple-assembling-iphone-15-brazil/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 15 開始巴西組裝，有望減輕當地消費者買機開支</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/iphone-shooting/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 以 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍攝【有片睇】手塚治蟲短片作品《Midnight》</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/vision-pro-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">郭明錤：Apple Vision Pro 無退貨潮，退貨率低於 1% 同 iPhone 15 Pro 相近</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/iphone-15-storage-dont-let-me-go/mobile-phone/">Apple 新廣告：iPhone 15 有足夠容量    「最低 128GB 起有足夠空間儲存相片」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
