            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223607</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>很多上班族都會受到腰痠背痛、雙腿痠軟之苦，放工後又時常做「低頭族」看手機螢幕，實在需要在空閒時放鬆一下。 Theragun 最近推出了 Theragun Pro Plus 及 Relief 按摩槍，讓大家可以隨時按摩放鬆身體。</p><h2>Theragun Pro Plus 按摩槍</h2><div class="block-main"><div id="entry-content-1164291" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Theragun Pro Plus 按摩槍使用 USB-C 充電，充滿電後最高可使用 150 分鐘。用家可控制每分鐘震動次數，震幅更達 16mm，有效衝擊深層肌肉組織。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可控制每分鐘震動次數</p><p>Theragun PRO Plus 更具備近紅外線 LED 燈 （near infrared LED light） 療程，通過設置於按摩槍槍頭下方手柄內的 13 個 LED 燈，在按摩時同時穿透皮膚照射肌肉組織，促進血液循環和細胞修復，有效增強衝擊療法的恢復效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲近紅外線 LED 燈</p></div><p>下圖是振動 （Vibration attachment）、減緩器 （Dampener） 、熱療 （Heated attachment）、楔形 （Wedge）、微點 （Micro-point）及姆指 （Thumb）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223833" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲旅行便攜袋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></div><p>熱療為新增設的槍頭，可在 10 秒自動升溫至 45°C、50 °C、55°C 的 3 種預設溫度，配合振動幅度較溫和的熱療模式，讓用家在運動訓練後緩解疼痛及減輕疲勞感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熱療槍頭</p><p>Theragun PRO Plus 手柄以三角型設計，方便無論握住任何位置均可保持平衡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三角設計</p><p>為方便用家調節振動頻率及強度，Theragun PRO Plus 在機身保留 LCD 顯示屏及實體操作鍵，操作數據一目瞭然。此外，按摩槍亦可通過藍牙連接 iOS 或 Android 專用手機應用程式，搜尋及下載更多適用的療程使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>產品規格</h2><table style="width: 100%; height: 536px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>體積 / 重量</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>36 x 154 x 65mm / 1.65kg （淨機身連內置電池,不包槍頭）</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>強度 / 振動頻率</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>5 級衝擊強度 / 3 種振動頻率</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 80px;"><td style="height: 80px;" width="132"><p>使用模式</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td><td style="height: 80px;" width="469"><p>衝擊治療、振動治療、近紅外線治療、熱療、呼吸訓練、冷療（須另購冷療槍頭）</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>使用時間</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>約 150 分鐘</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 208px;"><td style="height: 208px;" width="132"><p>隨盒配備</p></td><td style="height: 208px;"> </td><td style="height: 208px;" width="469"><p>Theragun PRO Plus 按摩槍：</p><p>6 種槍頭：標準球 （Standard Ball） 、姆指 （Thumb）、楔形（Wedge）、微點（Micro-point） 、振動 （Vibration attachment）、減緩器 （Dampener）及熱療 （Heated attachment）</p><p>旅行便攜袋、USB-C 充電線</p></td><td style="height: 208px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 80px;"><td style="height: 80px;" width="132"><p>其他功能</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td><td style="height: 80px;" width="469"><p>生物識別感應器、LCD 顯示屏、藍牙無線傳輸、連接 iOS 及 Android 專用手機應用程式</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>建議售價</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p style="text-align: left;">HK$4,899</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><h2>Theragun Relief 按摩槍</h2><p>Theragun Relief 同樣採用符合人體工學的三角手柄設計，無論用家握著三角形上任何一條手柄，都能保持絕佳平衡，可以更舒適及靈活地按摩身體不同部位。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223845" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲方便用家按摩不同位置</p><p>按摩槍提供 10mm 振動幅度按摩功能，配合跟機的 3 種按摩槍頭： 減緩器 （Dampener） 、標準球 （Standard Ball） 、姆指 （Thumb），可為全身不同肌肉進行按摩，紓緩日常疼痛並改善睡眠質素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223842" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>機身配備一個實體鍵，簡單易用。Theragun Relief 僅重 621g，方便隨身攜帶及在出國旅遊時使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全機身配備一粒按鈕，方便易用</p><p>Theragun Relief 機身輕巧和力度適中，特別適合女士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>產品規格</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>體積 / 重量</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>24.5 x 6.55 x 3.48mm / 621g （淨機身連內置電池）</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>使用模式</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>衝擊治療、呼吸訓練</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>使用時間</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>約 120 分鐘</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>隨盒配備</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>Theragun Relief 按摩槍、3 種槍頭：減緩器 （Dampener）、標準球（Standard Ball） 、姆指（Thumb）、USB-C 充電線</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>建議售價</p></td><td> </td><td style="text-align: left;" width="469">HK$1,199</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>總結：熱敷頭有效緩解肌肉痠痛，三角形手柄方便按摩刁鑽角度</h2><p>Theragun Pro Plus 配備多個按摩頭中，小編自己最喜歡的就是「熱療」和「微點」。「微點」按摩時可以有效放鬆繃緊的肌肉，按摩膊頭、腰部等位置非常舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223846" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲微點頭</p><p>而「熱療」就可在 10 秒自動升溫至 45°C、50 °C、55°C，配合 Theragun Pro Plus 按摩功能就可放鬆全身肌肉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熱療頭</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/theragun-pro-plus-relief/life-tech/">【實試】Theragun Pro Plus / Relief　發熱按摩功能 + 10mm 衝擊治療</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
